 has been made with the help of marble and other stones and <a href=\"https://aquanta.in/\"><strong>aquanta.in</strong></a> is the best online platform that exhibits the work of artisans, craftsperson, and designers who are passionate in their field of arts, crafts, décor, accessories and fashion. For example, a timepiece made up of makrana marble can be a perfect <img class=\" size-medium wp-image-59 alignleft\" src=\"https://aquanta.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/tajMahal-300x187.jpg\" alt=\"tajMahal\" width=\"300\" height=\"187\" />gift to someone on an occasion. It can also be used as a personal utility item. Such arts can be made up with various variations. The artisans use traditional colors to paint the marble giving it a prefect look. Also some can add single-colored or multicolored kundans. Such pieces are handcrafted thus they naturally have the antique look as well as they get attention from all because of its unique luster and combination.  Marble usually gives a royal look to anything it’s made into. The off-white color and other luster it possesses make it apt to make various articles out of it that can add the much needed facelift to the décor in your home.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://aquanta.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/makrana_marble.jpg\"><img class=\" size-medium wp-image-61 alignright\" src=\"https://aquanta.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/makrana_marble-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"makrana_marble\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a>Another example can be of a decorative marble plate made out of makrana marble. Using dark colors and various combinations of colors is surely a perfect art for making any corner of the room lively. Artisans use various themes which depict certain historic events. The Mughal theme depicted in the painting embellished with traditional colored kundans, gold and silver fine cut finishing is a perfect gift for your home and your loved ones.\r\n\r\nMarble crafts have always been the age old choice for craft lovers when i