tradesmen during the early era.\r\n\r\nToday quilling has become popular in every continent with people from all walks of life with its simple and creative possibilities. The essentials tools for quilling include slotted tool, needle tool, tweezers, and a circle sizer. For a beginner it is recommended they buy a beginners kit, since they will find all these aforementioned tools in it. Used to make wedding decorations, greeting cards, boxes, and scrapbook pages, quilling have become quite a famous form of art.\r\n\r\nAt <a href=\"http://www.kraftstory.com/\">Kraftstory</a> we celebrate this skill with some of our exclusive creations by (awaiting the name of the artist).\r\n\r\nHere are some of his incredible creations.\r\n\r\n1. White Board Magnet\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.kraftstory.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/4.png\"><img class=\" size-full wp-image-181 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.kraftstory.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/4.png\" alt=\"quilling or paper filigree\" width=\"700\" height=\"500\" /></a>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"> <a href=\"http://www.kraftstory.com/white-board-magnet-quilling\">Shop Now</a></p>\r\nJust what you wanted to list down your to do list, this useful fridge magnet with a marker is beauty with utility.\r\n\r\n2. Greeting Card\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.kraftstory.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/3.png\"><img class=\" size-full wp-image-180 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.kraftstory.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/3.png\" alt=\"quilling or paper filigree\" width=\"700\" height=\"500\" /></a>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"> <a href=\"http://www.kraftstory.com/handmade-quilled-greeting-card-en-6\">Shop Now</a></p>\r\nA 3D quilling card to make your special occasions all the more momentous.\r\n\r\n3. A Tea Light Holder\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.kraftstory.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/2.png\"><img class=\" size-full wp-image-179 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.kraftstory.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/2.png\" alt=\"quilling or paper filigree\" width=\"700\" height=\"500\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.kraftstory.com/handmade-tea-light-holder\">Shop Now</a></p>\r\nAn enchanting tea light holder handcrafted with paper quilling to give your home a unique touch.\r\n\r\n4. Hobby Board\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.kraftstory.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/1.png\"><img class=\" size-full wp-image-178 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.kraftstory.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/1.png\" alt=\"quilling or paper filigree\" width=\"700\" height=\"500\" /></a>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"> <a href=\"http://www.kraftstory.com/hobby-board-quilling\">Shop Now</a></p>\r\nNow fill in your wish list, for your hobbies or simply put down important tasks and use the pin board to pin bills or grocery list that you often tend to misplace.','Why We Love Quilling? And You Should Too','','publish','open','open','','why-we-love-quilling-and-you-should-too','','','2015-08-05 06:29:48','2015-08-05 06:29:48','',0,'https://www.kraftstory.com/blog/?p=177',0,'post','',0),(178,4,'2015-08-03 06:46:29','2015-08-03 06:46:29','','1','','inherit','open','open','','1-3','','','2015-08-03 06:46:46','2015-08-03 06:46:46','',177,'https://www.kraftstory.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(179,4,'2015-08-03 06:46:32','2015-08-03 06:46:32','','2','','inherit','open','open','','2-4','','','2015-08-03 06:46:50','2015-08-03 06:46:50','',177,'https://www.kraftstory.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(180,4,'2015-08-03 06:46:34','2015-08-03 06:46:34','','3','','inherit','open','open','','3-4','','','2015-08-03 06:46:54','2015-08-03 06:46:54','',177,'https://www.kraftstory.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/3.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(181,4,'2015-08-03 06:46:36','2015-08-03 06:46:36','','4','','inherit','open','open','','4-2','','','2015-08-03 06:46:59','2015-08-03 06:46:59','