t takes is the right dress and the rest of it just comes along.','Look Book: Celebrity Style to Adopt for Rakshabandhan','','inherit','open','open','','199-revision-v1','','','2015-08-21 11:26:36','2015-08-21 11:26:36','',199,'https://www.kraftstory.com/blog/199-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(215,4,'2015-08-31 09:24:57','2015-08-31 09:24:57','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.kraftstory.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/How-to-Wear-a-Saree-on-a-Regular-Day-at.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-220\" src=\"https://www.kraftstory.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/How-to-Wear-a-Saree-on-a-Regular-Day-at.png\" alt=\"Look Book\" width=\"540\" height=\"282\" /></a></p>\r\nToday is not Diwali or Dusshera. But can definitely be wear a saree to work day! Yes, it is not the trend of the time but why can you not make it one? Before getting into how you can do so, here are few reason why it is so easy to do so.\r\n<h3>Reasons You Should Wear a Saree to Work:</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Excellent attention grabber:</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\nWho doesn’t like a little attention? One small compliment can make anyone’s day. Well guess what? The day you wear a saree you will get more than just one compliment. A saree is one of those garments that brings out the beauty of a woman.\r\n<ol start=\"2\">\r\n	<li><strong>Adapts to your figure:</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\nA saree is the most versatile of all garments. It will make you look beautiful whether you are tall or short. If you are tall and slim, wrap it tightly around you with an unpleated pallu. It will enhance your height without making you look bony. On the other hand if you are stout wear it loosely with a pleated pallu. This will not make you look elegant and not bulky.\r\n<ol start=\"3\">\r\n	<li><strong>Comfort unmatched:</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\nUnlike what most people think, wearing a saree is actually hassle free. If you have worn it right, It will be easy to handle and roomy. If you don’t know how to wear a saree, there are lots of videos online that will teach you the right way.\r\n\r\nNow we aren’t saying wearing a saree is appropriate all the time. Nobody expects you to wear a saree while going to a pub. But wearing a saree to work from time to time is very much possible. If you convinced by the above reasons, take a look at what you could wear.\r\n<h3>Look 1: Modern Print</h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.kraftstory.com/clothing/sarees/casual-sarees/charming-geometrical-printed-bhagalpuri-silk-saree-32006\"><img class=\" size-full wp-image-217 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.kraftstory.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/21.png\" alt=\"modern saree\" width=\"180\" height=\"180\" /></a>The world of fashion is all about prints these days. Why not incorporate modern fashion to our traditional wear? This beautiful pink and white triveni geometrical printed silk saree is the perfect match! Its light weight which means it will be easy to handle throughout the day.  According to your level of comfort you can leave the pallu unpleated or pin it up.\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.kraftstory.com/jewellery/earrings/danglers/designer-pink-earrings\"><img class=\" size-full wp-image-219 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.kraftstory.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/41.png\" alt=\"designer pink earning\" width=\"180\" height=\"180\" /></a></p>\r\nSince you are going to work, you do not require a lot of accessories. Let the saree be the focus. These designer pink earning are the perfect balance of simple and elegant.\r\n\r\nLeave your hair down. Doesn’t matter if you have curly or straight hair, they will both look beautiful.  As for make up, keep it simple.\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Apply a light layer of foundation.</li>\r\n	<li>Apply eyeliner. You could choose to do a simple look or opt for the winged liner.</li>\r\n	<li>Apply a few coats of mascara</li>\r\n	<li>Apply a little blush on the apple of your cheeks</li>\r\n	<li>Apply a rose color lipstick.</li>\r\n	<li>Finish the look by apply a compact</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nSlip on a pair of flat sandals for ultimate comfort and you will be turning heads where ever you go.\r\n<h3>Look 2: Color Block</h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.kraftstory.com/clothing/sarees/casual-sarees/triveni-adorable-black-colored-printed-satin-silk-saree\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-216 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.kraftstory.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/11.png\" alt=\"cobalt and black printed saree\" width=\"180\" height=\"180\" /></a>\r\n\r\nColor blocking is another fashion trend and we say blend trendy with traditional! This adorable cobalt and black printed saree could be your step to try this trend.\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.kraftstory.com/jewellery/earrings/danglers/silver-glaze-earrings-with-paisley-design-and-blue-drop\"><img class=\" size-full wp-image-218 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.kraftstory.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/31.png\" alt=\"3\" width=\"180\" height=\"180\" /></a></p>\r\nThis too is lightweight and will be very easy to handle. Wear it with the pallu pinned up or leave it down. Stand out even more with these stunning blue drop earrings.\r\n\r\nLeave your hair down or swept to one side to show off your earrings and your hair is done as well. And since the saree is so vibrant keep the makeup simple.\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Apply foundation</li>\r\n	<li>Apply eyeliner</li>\r\n	<li>Apply a few coats of mascara</li>\r\n	<li>Finally, apply your favorite shade of lipstick and you are good to go.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nSlip on a pair of blue flat sandals and walk to your desk knowing you look stunning.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWearing a saree to work doesn’t have to be a hassle. Choose a beautiful saree, keep the makeup simple and walk out of the house ready in just a matter of minutes.','Look Book: How to Wear a Saree on a Regular Day at Work','','publish','open','open','','look-book-how-to-wear-a-saree-on-a-