er-vase-4588\"><img class=\" size-full wp-image-243 alignleft\" src=\"https://www.kraftstory.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/CHFV-5062.jpg\" alt=\"CHFV-5062\" width=\"140\" height=\"140\" /></a>\r\n\r\nThe festive season is all about lights and colors. Add some royal colors to you house with this  beautiful marble vase. It can be placed in a corner and yet will be a talked about décor piece. The  elegance of the peacock and the brightness of the stones is the perfect combination for attention!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><span lang=\"EN-US\">For the love of comfort</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"https://www.kraftstory.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/Untitled-design-1.png\"><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-249\" src=\"https://www.kraftstory.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/Untitled-design-1-150x150.png\" alt=\"buy custom cushion covers\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>Add some ethnic touch to you room with these printed cushion covers. It will add some color and fun to your room. They are made with azo-free dyes making them easy to maintain and environment friendly. The <a href=\"http://www.kraftstory.com/home-decor/cushions-throws/covers-furnishings/indian-king-cushion-cover\">king</a> and the <a href=\"http://www.kraftstory.com/home-decor/cushions-throws/covers-furnishings/indian-queen-cushion-cover\">queen</a> would be a great addition to your home, isn’t it?</p>\r\n\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2>Pooja Room</h2>\r\nThe next room that people will visit is the beloved pooja room. Every house decorates their pooja room with a lot of love and care. It doesn’t matter if the room is big or small, the fondness still stays. There are a lot of poojas and artis that will happen now with the onset of the festive season. Why not show some more love to the deity you love?\r\n<h3>For incense</h3>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.kraftstory.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/2.png\"><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-250\" src=\"https://www.kraftstory.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/2-150x150.png\" alt=\"incense stick stand\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>The pleasant smell that engulfs the house once an agarbatti is lit cannot be denied. Lighting an agarbatti is also part of many artis. Try this unique and <a href=\"http://www.kraftstory.com/haathi-agarbatti-stand\">ethic agarbatti stand</a> instead of the older one. It has miniature elephants and mehendi work on the bottom.  If you are a lover of details, maybe this <a href=\"http://www.kraftstory.com/home-decor/spiritual/prayer-accessories/kundan-embellished-marble-incense-holder\">kundan embellished incense holder</a>. The traditional colors will add more beauty to the pooja place.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3>For Arti</h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.kraftstory.com/home-decor/spiritual/pooja-thalis/ecraftindia-golden-marble-pooja-thali-with-swastik\"><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-246\" src=\"https://www.kraftstory.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/MOPT1007-other-1-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"Aarthi Thali\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a> Preparing the pooja thali has never been easier! These beautiful marble pooja thalis have a  place for everything. It’s also a piece of art with all the detailed work that has been done on  them. This thali is handcrafted by skilled artisans using traditional techniques. There will be  lots of questions to answer once the aarti is done, that is a given.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThe bright season of festivals will only get brighter with these additions to your house!','What can you do different for your home this festive season!','','inherit','open','open','','237-revision-v1','','','2015-09-30 13:32:06','2015-09-30 13:32:06','',237,'https://www.kraftstory.com/blog/237-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(253,4,'2015-10-14 10:13:16','2015-10-14 10:13:16','','logo','','inherit','open',