6:04','2015-12-03 10:56:04','','Bring The Stars To Your Style!','','inherit','open','open','','bring-the-stars-to-your-style','','','2015-12-03 10:56:04','2015-12-03 10:56:04','',356,'http://blog.kraftstory.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Bring-The-Stars-To-Your-Style.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(360,4,'2015-12-04 10:49:22','2015-12-04 10:49:22','<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When it comes to ethnic wear in India, there are many different types of varieties and options. Being an all-time favourite especially among Punjabi girls, Patiala suits have always been popular not only in India but in other countries as well. This pleated trouser style suit if actually stitched to perfection can give you the balance of style and elegance! But what exactly is stitching it perfection? What exactly is a Patiala suit? </span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What is a Patiala Suit?</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A loosely fitted pajama which has numerous pleats at the bottom, a Patiala Suit has always been signified by royalty. Due to the double amount of cloth required to stitch a Patiala salwar, the wearer of this salwar is considered among the upper class. A Patiala Salwar has a baggy look with a beautiful fall. The pleats are stitched in such a way that they meet at the ankle making it look casual yet elegant. Due to its origin and the amount of cloth required to stitch a Patiala Salwar, it is also named as the Patiala Shahi Salwar.</span>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.kraftstory.com/clothing/kurta-salwar/patiala-suits-online-shopping/patiala-style-unstitched-salwar-suit-of-kurta-orange-color-and-salwar-of-multi-colour-color\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\" size-full wp-image-361 aligncenter\" src=\"http://blog.kraftstory.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/31925_2.jpg\" alt=\"31925_2\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></a>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What is its origin? </span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A Patiala Suit is as old as a Salwar Kameez. It was originally invented as the royal dress for the Nawab of Patiala and that is where it got its name from. During the historic times Patiala Salwars was actually designed for men. Later on, the trend evolved and the Patiala Suit entered the women fashion. You can still view the age old Patiala suits in the Darjiya Wali Gali to witness the true richness of a well-stitched gorgeous Patiala Suit. You can also buy these rich and elegant Patiala Suits by online shopping. The fabrics used in that age however cannot be used today.</span>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.kraftstory.com/clothing/kurta-salwar/patiala-suits-online-shopping/patiala-style-unstitched-salwar-suit-of-kurta-red-color-and-salwar-of-grey-color\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\" size-full wp-image-364 aligncenter\" src=\"http://blog.kraftstory.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/31923_2.jpg\" alt=\"31923_2\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What Fabric to wear?</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The most important aspect of a Patiala Suit is the fabric. Without the correct fabric, the salwar will look like a worn down pair of loose trousers. While picking a fabric for a Patiala suit you must keep in mind the texture, it has got to be rich. Fabrics like cotton, crepe, silk, georgette and brocade will work magic on a Patiala Suit. Although special care of the fabric should be taken while buying a Patiala Suit through online shopping.  </span>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.kraftstory.com/clothing/kurta-salwar/patiala-suits-online-shopping/patiala-style-unstitched-salwar-suit-of-kurta-yellow-color-and-salwar-of-yellow-color\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\" size-full wp-image-363 aligncenter\" src=\"http://blog.kraftstory.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/31914_2.jpg\" alt=\"31914_2\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></a>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What is the Current Trend?</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When Rani Mukherjee dressed in a beautiful Patiala salwar along with a short collar style kurta, it was all everyone was talking about. Over the period the style of a Patiala suit has evolved tremendously. Giving the attire a more modern twist, designers have now given the top of a Patiala suit a more tunic style appearance and the salwar is replaced with modern style dhoti pants making the look more casual and gorgeous. There are a lot of varieties available when you purchase a Patiala suit online shopping. </span>\r\n\r\n<strong><strong> </strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Be it the village girls or the modern girls of the city, a Patiala suit makes every woman look traditional yet fashionable. Being comfortable to wear on a daily basis and stylish and elegant enough to wear in weddings, functions and ceremonies, Patiala suits are perfect for every occasion. With this truly ethnic style of dressing, stay updated with fashion today! </span>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"www.kraftstory.com\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-339\" src=\"http://blog.kraftstory.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/KRAFTSTORY.jpg\" alt=\"KRAFTSTORY\" width=\"804\" height=\"466\" /></a>','Punjabi’s Pride – Everything you need to know about Patiala Suits!','','publish','open','open','','punjabis-pride-everything-you-need-to-know-about-patiala-suits','','','2015-12-04 10:49:22','2015-12-04 10:49:22','',0,'http://blog.kraftstory.com/?p=360',0,'post','',0),(361,4,'2015-12-04 10:45:20','2015-12-04 10:45:20','','31925_2','','inherit','open','open','','31925_2','','','2015-12-04 10:45:20','2015-12-04 10:45:20','',360,'http://blog.kraftstory.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/31925_2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(362,4,'2015-12-04 10:45:22','2015-12-04 10:45:22','','Punjabi’s Pride – Everything you need to know about Patiala Suits!','','inherit','open','open','','punjabis-pride-everything-you-need-t