48:53','2015-12-07 10:48:53','There are far too many types of fabric available all around the world. But there are some that are done by hand. Here are some of those.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://blog.kraftstory.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/handmade-fabric-infographic.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-367\" src=\"http://blog.kraftstory.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/handmade-fabric-infographic.png\" alt=\"handmade fabric infographic\" width=\"1200\" height=\"2972\" /></a>','The Lost World Of Handmade Fabric! (Infographic)','','publish','open','open','','the-lost-world-of-handmade-fabric-infographic','','','2015-12-07 10:48:53','2015-12-07 10:48:53','',0,'http://blog.kraftstory.com/?p=366',0,'post','',0),(367,1,'2015-12-07 10:38:30','2015-12-07 10:38:30','','handmade fabric infographic','','inherit','open','open','','handmade-fabric-infographic','','','2015-12-07 10:38:30','2015-12-07 10:38:30','',366,'http://blog.kraftstory.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/handmade-fabric-infographic.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(368,1,'2015-12-07 10:44:31','2015-12-07 10:44:31','','HANDMADE FABRIC FEATURE IMAGE','','inherit','open','open','','handmade-fabric-feature-image','','','2015-12-07 10:44:31','2015-12-07 10:44:31','',366,'http://blog.kraftstory.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/HANDMADE-FABRIC-FEATURE-IMAGE.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(369,1,'2015-12-07 10:44:50','2015-12-07 10:44:50','There are far too many types of fabric available all around the world. But there are some that are done by hand. Here are some of those.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://blog.kraftstory.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/handmade-fabric-infographic.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-367\" src=\"http://blog.kraftstory.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/handmade-fabric-infographic.png\" alt=\"handmade fabric infographic\" width=\"1200\" height=\"2972\" /></a>','The Lost World Of Handmade Fabric! (Infographic)','','inherit','open','open','','366-revision-v1','','','2015-12-07 10:44:50','2015-12-07 10:44:50','',366,'http://blog.kraftstory.com/366-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(370,1,'2015-12-16 14:10:02','2015-12-16 14:10:02','<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We know how frustrating it can be to decide on one idea when you are playing with the idea of revamping your home! A number of ideas that storm through your mind can be really hard to sort through. Don\'t worry we are here to help!. Today we present KraftStory’s selection of  home décor ideas only for you to wow you homes. </span>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li> <b><b>Add interest with light</b></b></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nBelieve us a few good light sources can light up any room in your house. They are a small investment and yet deliver with enough power to change the look of your house. The best way to add light to your house is using lamps. We have a number of lamps for you to choose from. If you love the minimalistic look we have plain geometric lamps or if you like colors then we have some beautifully printed lamps for you to choose from. Mix it up with a good painting or a wall piece and turn that empty corner into an art zone.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://blog.kraftstory.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/1.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-377\" src=\"http://blog.kraftstory.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/1.png\" alt=\"1\" width=\"945\" height=\"756\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><b>Elegant rooms with rugs and carpets!</b></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nRugs and carpets add a touch of elegance and warmth to any room they are placed in! If you are not ready to change the entire look of your home but still want to do a change, then this is the route for you. Carpets and rugs instantly change the look of your house without being a huge investment. Place them in a bedroom or in the hall, they surely will spruce up the place and cozy up the place. We have rugs and carpets in a lot of patterns and colors for you to choose from. Here are few examples of what we have to offer.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://blog.kraftstory.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/2.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-378\" src=\"http://blog.kraftstory.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/2.png\" alt=\"2\" width=\"945\" height=\"756\" /></a>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><b>Change the drapes for a new look</b></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The first thing that you put up and the last thing you change are probably your curtains. People don’t usually think of these long pieces of cloth to change the look of their house. But these are yet again are one of the less expensive ways to bring the change you desire. Try out different patterns for different looks. Who says you have to stick to plain old solid colors. These days it’s all about patterns and prints. Here are a few interesting conversation starters you can incorporate to your home. </span>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://blog.kraftstory.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/3.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-379\" src=\"http://blog.kraftstory.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/3.png\" alt=\"3\" width=\"945\" height=\"756\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><b>Add some dimension with mirrors and frames</b></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe bet you never thought that hanging decorative mirrors and frames would change up your houses look! But it does, oh so well! They add an element of interest in the otherwise monotone hues of a room. Imagine your hall is designed around the color brown. Now add a few strategically placed mirrors and colorful works of art. Boom! Interest and dimension. Here are few ideas you can be inspired by.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://blog.kraftstory.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/5.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-381\" src=\"http://blog.kraftstory.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/5.png\" alt=\"5\" width=\"945\" height=\"756\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Comfort with cushions</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cushions, something we associate with the bed and sleeping. But over the past few years this source of comfort has made its way to the hall as well. Add color and spunk to your hall by throwing some contrasting cushions on to your couch! Here are a few for you to look at. We have a lot more! </span>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://blog.kraftstory.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/4.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-380\" src=\"http://blog.kraftstory.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/4.png\" alt=\"4\" width=\"945\" height=\"756\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>Decorating your home doesn’t have to be rocket science! We hope our list helped you to make some décor decisions.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Thinking of decking your house up? Here are a few ideas to make your life easy!','','publish','open','open','','thinking-of-decking-your-house-up-here-are-a-few-ideas-to-make-your-life-easy','','','2015-12-08 06:49:23','2015-12-08 06:49:23','',0,'http://blog.kraftstory.com/?p=370',0,'post','',0),(371,1,'2015-12-08 06:08:45','2015-12-08 06:08:45','','lamp','','inherit','open','open','','lamp-1','','','2015-12-08 06:08:52','2015-12-08 06:08:52','',370,'http://blog.kraftstory.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/lamp-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(372,1,'2015-12-08 06:08:46','2015-12-08 06:08:46','','lamp','','inherit','open','open','','lamp-2','','','2015-12-08 06:08:54','2015-12-08 06:08:54','',370,'http://blog.kraftstory.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/lamp-2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(373,1,'2015-12-08 06:08:48','2015-12-08 06:08:48','','lamp','','inherit','open','open','','lamp-3','','','2015-12-08 06:08:57','2015-12-08 06:08:57','',370,'http://blog.kraftstory.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/lamp-3.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(374,1,'2015-12-08 06:08:49','2015-12-08 06:08:49','','lamp','','inherit','open','open','','lamp-4','','','2015-12-08 06:09:00','2015-12-08 06:09:00','',370,'http://blog.kraftstory.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/lamp-4.jpg',0,'attachment','